<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:padding="24dp"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent">

    <Space
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="143dp" />

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/textView"
        android:text="Waiting for QR..."
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content" />

    <Button
        android:id="@+id/sendButton"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginTop="16dp"
        android:text="Scan Code Again" />
    To achieve this, you’ll need to update your XML layout with a TextView for the selection status and a GridLayout for the 3x3 element grid. You will also need a selector drawable to handle the border color change logic and some Kotlin/Java code to enforce the "max 3" rule.
    1. The Updated XML Layout

    Add these elements below your existing Button. Note the use of GridLayout for the 3x3 structure.
    XML

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/selectedElementsText"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginTop="24dp"
        android:text="Selected: None"
        android:textSize="16sp"
        android:textStyle="bold" />

    <GridLayout
        android:id="@+id/elementGrid"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginTop="16dp"
        android:columnCount="3"
        android:rowCount="3"
        android:alignmentMode="alignMargins"
        android:columnOrderPreserved="false">

        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Fire"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Wind"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Death"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Life"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Gravity"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Gravity"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Darkness"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Light"
            android:background="@drawable/element_button_selector"
            android:layout_margin="4dp" />
        <Button
            android:layout_width="0dp"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_columnWeight="1"
            android:text="Spirit"
